<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Testimonio Matías Muñoz</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}

body{
background:transparent;
font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
color:#fff;
padding:8px 0;
}

.player{
width:100%;
max-width:980px;
margin:0 auto;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
gap:18px;
}

button{
width:58px;
height:58px;
border-radius:50%;
border:2px solid #fff;
background:transparent;
color:#fff;
font-size:22px;
cursor:pointer;
flex-shrink:0;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
padding-left:3px;
}

.info{flex:1;min-width:0;}

.text{
font-size:24px;
line-height:1.28;
margin-bottom:12px;
max-width:860px;
color:#fff;
}

.wave{
width:100%;
height:42px;
display:flex;
align-items:flex-end;
gap:4px;
}

.wave span{
flex:1;
background:#fff;
border-radius:20px;
opacity:.95;
min-width:3px;
}

.wave span:nth-child(6n+1){height:12px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+2){height:26px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+3){height:42px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+4){height:20px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+5){height:34px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+6){height:16px;}

.playing .wave span{animation:wave .8s ease-in-out infinite;}
.playing .wave span:nth-child(even){animation-delay:.15s;}
.playing .wave span:nth-child(3n){animation-delay:.3s;}

@keyframes wave{
0%,100%{transform:scaleY(.6);}
50%{transform:scaleY(1.15);}
}

@media(max-width:700px){
.player{gap:14px;}
button{width:48px;height:48px;font-size:18px;}
.text{font-size:19px;}
.wave{height:34px;}
.wave span:nth-child(6n+3){height:34px;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="player" id="player">
<button id="play" type="button">▶</button>

<div class="info">
<div class="text">
¿Qué impacto tiene la incertidumbre en la salud mental<br>
de quienes hacen ciencia? Escucha el testimonio de Matías Muñoz.
</div>

<div class="wave">
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
<span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<audio id="audio" preload="auto">
<source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/disriewal/video/upload/v1782514818/Cun%CC%83a_Mati%CC%81as_Audio_Mental_ffxmtx.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<script>
const audio = document.getElementById("audio");
const btn = document.getElementById("play");
const player = document.getElementById("player");

btn.onclick = () => {
  if (audio.paused) {
    audio.play();
    btn.innerHTML = "❚❚";
    btn.style.paddingLeft = "0";
    player.classList.add("playing");
  } else {
    audio.pause();
    btn.innerHTML = "▶";
    btn.style.paddingLeft = "3px";
    player.classList.remove("playing");
  }
};

audio.onended = () => {
  btn.innerHTML = "▶";
  btn.style.paddingLeft = "3px";
  player.classList.remove("playing");
};
</script>

</body>
</html>
